<p style="margin-top: 1rem;">We handle 43+ language pairs with Arabic-English being the most common for UAE use. Whether your documents originate from India, Pakistan, Philippines, UK, USA, or any other country, our translators understand both the source language nuances and UAE authority formatting requirements.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Why clients choose our translation services:</strong></p>
<ul style="margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
<li><strong>Pre-submission review</strong> — We check your documents before you pay to ensure they meet requirements for your intended use</li>
<li><strong>Authority-specific formatting</strong> — Each translation is formatted for its destination, whether Dubai Courts, DIFC, DLD, or immigration</li>
<li><strong>Same-day delivery</strong> — Standard documents complete in 4-6 hours with express options for urgent deadlines</li>
<li><strong>Acceptance guarantee</strong> — If any government entity rejects our translation due to our error, we correct and redeliver at no charge</li>
</ul>

<p>From single-page birth certificates to complex multi-document Golden Visa packages, our process remains the same: submit via WhatsApp, receive instant quote, approve, and get certified translations delivered digitally with optional courier delivery anywhere in the UAE.</p>`}
